node.text: **Mama Jen here...it's with heavy heart that I must announce that the girls and I are leaving our beloved Nogginland home 😢🏡 I am devastated,and I keep wishing that our current situation, wasn't that at all 😢This is extremely difficult for us as this has always been our home and it was literally built and designed just for them 🙏🏻 It's where our Ramp House is,our Nog House resides,and its got custom built ramps throughout since Igloo can't do stairs 😢Most importantly, it is a place that holds so many memories for us,and especially for me,as the memories made here with my mom and Kelsey,are ones that I'll never have the opportunity to make again 😢That said, we must go,so I am determined to make this transition as smooth as possible for my girls as we face this next chapter in our life. We will be moving out of NY, something that I've never done before,so it's going to be a big adjustment for the three of us for sure. 😢I've worked tirelessly to secure something that I can hopefully manage alone and I finally found a rental home with no stairs for my little Loo. 🙏🏻I will be taking the next few weeks off from here to focus solely on moving and making sure that my girls know that I am NOT going anywhere. That no matter where we live, as long as we have eachother, we will make it beautiful 💓When we do return we will most likely be posting a mixture of new and old pics/videos so please be patient with us while we try and adapt to our new and unfamiliar environment. 🙏🏻I won't be responding to any comments or DM's, as my pain is too great, but please please know how incredibly much we love and appreciate you ALL, day in and day out💓You are my family and after losing so much these past few years, you have all honesty made me feel, like I'm never alone 🙏🏻Thank you for loving us and we hope that you will bear with our brief absence and will be here, ready and waiting for us, to triumphantly return 💓Happy #TransformationTuesday my loves 🏡Change isn't always something that we want, but sometimes it's something that we need 🙏🏻💓 We love you so very much and promise that we will see you real soon 💓💋 -Jen, Eggnog and Igloo 🏡❄️

.

Nothing screams Saturday like some burning questions, your favorite beer and your very best friend....🐶💖 #ad 🍺 It's definitely been a tough year for all of us and let's be honest, if it wasn't for our dogs, things may have been a lot more difficult 🐶That's why us pups deserve a pawsome appreciation pawty!! 🎉🙌🏻🐶 Well thankfully @lagunitasbeer is gifting 100 lucky winners an amazing Lagunitas Doggy Boondoggle Party Pack in honor of International Dog Day on 8/26!! 🙌🏻 From now until 7/23 post a video or pic explaining why your dog deserves a party and hashtag it #LagunitasDogContest 🐶 Head to their website to register your entry and you are good to go! 🙌🏻🎉🐶 We are keeping our paws crossed that you are among the winners! 🐾Happy weekend everyone! 🐶🍺💖#LagunitasBrewing #PaidInBeer #BeerSpeaksDogsDrool #ad21+.
.
.
.
